{"tid":1775980,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【玩死TVB行動】 - 中旅社嘅安信wewa剪卡挑戰2.0","createTime":"2019-12-09T08:06:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T11:58:50.000Z","uid":113630,"like":61,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"1bdc01328c33c0ec16495d0db4d0b5bf84bfc4ae","tid":1775980,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T08:06:46.000Z","msg":"😈【新一波玩死TVB行動 - wewa剪卡挑戰2.0】 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/akN8BuW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FakN8BuW.png&h=e4a8d20b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n#wewachallenge #打擊TVB財仔廣告 #財仔廣告好好賺  <br />\n<br />\n經過上次嘅剪卡行動後，安信暫停咗一排TVB廣告，依家又見返❗️😒  <br />\n仲記唔記得，4年前Mastercard搵唯萎賣廣告掀起剪卡狂潮^，今次安信賣TVB廣告，我哋要點做❓🙃  <br />\nTVB第二大廣告客戶類別就係貸款及按揭公司*，抵制是常識吧～不過財務公司好難抵制，其中一個大客就係安信，呢排係咁喺TVB賣廣告，佢哋有張wewa卡成日sell大學生申請，所以可能好多後生仔都有一張，有咭嘅手足一定可以參與❗️ 冇卡嘅都可以幫手洗板！  <br />\n<br />\n1️⃣剪卡 ☎️首先打去客戶服務熱線申請取消，2111 2999 快捷鍵︰1 &gt; 3 &gt; 8 ✂️打完就可安心剪卡。為安全起見，記住剪爛卡上嘅磁帶同晶片。 上次有幾位手足響應剪卡，但係可惜FB玩嘢，幾張剪卡相都睇唔到😩 <br />\n2️⃣ Up 上FB （冇卡嘅就洗板） 剪完卡，用返舊招：😡1.派嬲 🗣2.洗版 <br />\n📷3. 擺張剪卡相上wewa FB （有咭適用 傳送門）：<br />\n 👉🏻<a href=\"https://facebook.com/安信兄弟-20044405381/posts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2F%E5%AE%89%E4%BF%A1%E5%85%84%E5%BC%9F-20044405381%2Fposts&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2LdUcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=f402a5ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://facebook.com/安信兄弟-20044405381/posts</a><br />\n 👉🏻<a href=\"https://facebook.com/WeWaMode/posts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2FWeWaMode%2Fposts&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2LdUcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=91d51d41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://facebook.com/WeWaMode/posts</a>  <br />\n仲要，擺喺自己status度 hashtag #wewachallenge，再tag @WeWa玩嘢Mode，標題寫「安信兄弟資助TVB假新聞，恥與為伍」，當然要轉地球公開Post。  <br />\n各位手足應該樂見TVB失去財仔大客，快啲參加wewa卡挑戰啦❗️ <br />\n***  <br />\nSource：<br />\n ^梁烈唯掀起剪Mastercard熱潮 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2PuO0GJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2PuO0GJ&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2LdUcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=5c90f091\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2PuO0GJ</a> <br />\n*TVB認客戶押後廣告 稱無重大影響 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2E0YqIy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2E0YqIy&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2LdUcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=0710df95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2E0YqIy</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">歡迎用呢幅圖留言</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pNa95n7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpNa95n7.png&h=f0848e48&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔講唔知安信嘅大股東原來係中旅社呀！咁客戶個人資料咪危危乎？😰</span></strong><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1u619D6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1u619D6.png&h=ffeb70a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N5j3qqa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN5j3qqa.png&h=29a870ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uDAJSCj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuDAJSCj.jpg&h=2d7096c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/POcTvpd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPOcTvpd.png&h=5d2bbbd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4OFB5XW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4OFB5XW.jpg&h=34f0d91a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記得bookmark</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: TVB廣告客戶名單！！</strong></span>  <br />\n<br />\n消費前諗清楚  <br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2P7cPe